translations: adj.键控的；有键的；定在某调的

sentences.sentence: Brian keyed in his personal code.
sentences.translation: 布赖恩键入了他的个人密码。

sentences.sentence: I wasn't able to sleep that night, I was so keyed up.
sentences.translation: 那一夜我无法入睡，我太激动了。

sentences.sentence: The classes are keyed to the needs of advanced students.
sentences.translation: 这些课是针对高年级学生的需要开设的。
